Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.60,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}暗夜之晓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.10,0:24:54.94,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\be1}明天 会到来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传遍我全身的暗黑魔力  真是令人怀念的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉泽萝忒·薇露库麦丝塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望  就由我来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来视吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为魂魄  与所爱之人永远游荡在世间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让你得到「碎片」了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯佩尔比亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼之主杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至极  事到如今还无法接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉泽萝忒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要斩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会忘了我是不死之躯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在「碎片」已经不足  能实现你愿望的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我这右眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么能救结花  救大家和世界的方法只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我死就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢故事的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「从那以后两个人便在一起  过上了幸福的生活」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里是没什么  怎么了？出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君  去公园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在房间里读书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃点东西比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  摔扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去要点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有结花陪你呢  有结花陪你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美铃前辈…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该感谢结花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你把雷切顶到脖子前的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花用能力将雷切消灭  你才得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉泽萝忒也失去了战斗能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然只是暂时性的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞趁机把我们转移到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是使用能力而疲劳  还有受到刺激了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱  竟然想自尽  你真是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「从那以后两个人便在一起  过上了幸福的生活」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为自己明白了  却是一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能消失  不管发生什么事都不能离开结花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我的命还在  我要偿还结花所给我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随我的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我要打倒莉泽萝忒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要命还在…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是结花造出来的幻影吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不是在结花的世界里的菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿布拉库萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寄宿在驱的姐姐身上的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐身上的精灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主人菊理自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她认为虚无的碎片只要少一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女莉泽萝忒的野心就不能实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱的姐姐知道地狱之坠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道  所以我的主人才会杀掉劫之眼的主人  她的弟弟驱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而自己也自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？驱可是还活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  驱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿布拉库萨斯曾经杀了驱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那并不是拥有劫之眼的驱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有劫之眼的驱不是在菊理的世界里  而是在其他世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花的世界吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是  所以你才活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花的世界里的菊理并没有「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有阿布拉库萨斯  所以才只有她一个死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全搞不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  两个不同世界里的菊理都知晓了同一个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采取了一样的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有「碎片」的那个用精灵阿布拉库萨斯把驱杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是结花的世界里的菊理并没有精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能亲手杀掉驱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个驱就是你  你才是劫之眼的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来你应该是和拥有「碎片」的菊理一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知在什么阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花用「碎片」的力量把你召唤到了自己的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意之间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁告诉菊理的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是两个  在除了赤夜之外的六个世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都把事实告诉了菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能特定在哪个世界里的菊理是「碎片」的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跨越时空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你只把事实告诉菊理？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我接受指令的那时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了菊理之外的「碎片」的主人都太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对姐姐说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「为了拯救世界  你就去死吧」是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是做了下警告而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没想到  结局会是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静  驱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都感到非常内疚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是从来都没有扯上过关系就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是赤夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的主人在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是把结花的力量给封印住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皐月驱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎已经没有想要自行了断的意思了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把结花还来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  你就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真老实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你把结花还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱…  君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑月正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  一起坠入地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该相信黑骑士们的转变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混账
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把我的…  碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她不是人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过除了心以外  都是人造的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以生命为代价的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有这个的话  说不定封印还能够完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞她拥有穿越时空的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这能力的基础上  再加以劫之眼的力量的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能够将莉泽萝忒封印在时空的夹缝之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得一试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要救驱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要杀他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界的可能性  已经无限接近于零
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  相信一次  也未尝不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间供我们争辩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以阿瓦利提亚大人现在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无法长时间维持封印的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再做无谓的挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能保护你  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  结花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保护别人的  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护好结花的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后  直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深锁总光之门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七惑七星所召
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由自草丘之势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武曲零零
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁之侣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真打  童子切安纲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:17:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噬命之刀  童子切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会成为驱你的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  你也对驱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底还是人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是毁灭  还是守护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归根结底  都是由心做主呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦利提亚大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  就让一切结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不允许结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是起点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望  只不过是为了品尝绝望而生的  愚蠢的梦境而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明好不容易才觉察到了自己的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明好不容易才决定要从此改变自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你为什么又要把明天就此抹去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管谁叫我放手  我都绝不言弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有人说  希望的尽头  只有绝望在等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也决不会相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世事有好亦有坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世人有善亦有恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是如今不如意  亲手改变就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放弃了  不就万事皆休了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你听来  也许这只不过是孩子的戏言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我却真心实意地这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信着明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾以为自己是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也以为自己是靠着一己之力独活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  事实却并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我身后  一直都有人在支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有结花在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为有结花在我身边  我才没有迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是结花的功劳呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我和结花的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都将由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真能守护得住  你就守来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉泽萝忒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉德？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念  从劫之眼里头…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能夺走这些人的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉德…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前  我看不到世人的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个少年告诉了我这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能明白  莉泽萝忒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以抹杀这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维拉德…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不会再犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我苦忍了八百年的孤独  想要的便只有这…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠玉碑的碎片  劫之眼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快集气  美铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童子哟童子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食我血肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身化魔炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪我现世之大怨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无用的抵抗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可能让你得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远地睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴比伦的魔女！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦利提亚大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结…  结花…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了主人的赤夜  已经开始崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有这样的未来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁家就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  驱君你啊  又跟结花来孤男寡女啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行  不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让人家也甜蜜蜜  疯颠颠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说些神经兮兮的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后  我和结花  都没有再提过赤夜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开那个大不倒翁一看  里面又出来了一个小不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再打开那小不倒翁一看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:23:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有一个更小的不倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:23:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又擅自从我钱包里顺手牵羊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.06,0:24:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  贤久前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话还没说完呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得用身体来还债  贤久
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就150日元嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,150日元还嫌少  你给我站住…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.83,0:24:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子和贤久也不知道我们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里  既没有菊理姐  也没有栞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.54,0:24:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美铃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.06,0:24:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去阿亚纳斯逛逛  要是方便的话  能不能陪我一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.06,0:24:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs17}注：阿亚纳斯商场所在的位置正好是赤夜中水晶塔的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.64,0:24:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道这是谁的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.00,0:24:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在这里  却有一份安乐与平静
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.38,0:24:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.85,0:24:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.92,0:24:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那不是未来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.10,0:24:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个世界  便还会拥有明天


